{
 "name": "RPlog_Perfectly_Balanced_as_All_Things_Should_Be",
 "title": "Perfectly Balanced, as All Things Should Be",
 "summary": "Amidst the wreckage of the destroyed station Pride-1, the doctor Lynae Cassius docks with the Sith Malus aboard his refreshed YT-1300 freighter, the Revenant. Malus reaches out with the Force to confirm she has come alone before welcoming her into the red-lit, Imperial-grey corridors of his ship. The two trade careful, clinical conversation -- on tactical lighting, prosthetics, and the cybernetic eye Lynae bears -- as he guides her toward the crew lounge for their meeting. The encounter sets a poised, watchful tone between the wary doctor and the calculating Sith.",
